</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-72_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">CIM advocates on behalf of marketers, ensuring their interests are represented in policy discussions. It also provides a wealth of resources, including guidelines, toolkits, and case studies, to help marketers implement best practices effectively.



































